{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckbox"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckbox"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"anchor":"Indicator-states","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Indicator states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This checkbox indicator has two available states:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you need to use a tri-state checkbox instead, refer to "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"anchor":"Particular-cases","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Particular cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}]},{"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","level":2,"text":"Cases forbidden by design"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or a read only situation and a disabled component."}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2,"text":"Code samples"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have a selected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = true","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Suggestions","level":2,"text":"Suggestions"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":", the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unified-design-system.orange.com"}],"isActive":true,"type":"reference","overridingTitle":"unified-design-system.orange.com","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox"}]},{"anchor":"Themes-rendering","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Themes rendering"},{"anchor":"Orange","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"anchor":"Orange-Compact","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Orange Compact"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading","text":"Sosh"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_Sosh","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe","level":3,"text":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_Wireframe","type":"image"}]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Version","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}]},{"name":"Since","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"sectio